<para style="p">For the chief musician; set to the gittith style. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Yahweh our Lord, how magnificent is your name in all the earth,</para>

<para style="q1">you who reveal your glory in the heavens above.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Out of the mouth of babies and infants you have created praise</para>

<para style="q1">because of your adversaries,</para>

<para style="q1">in order to silence both the enemy and the avenger.</para>
